The paper discusses the construction of a barrier certificate for a control affine system subject to actuator constraints, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY). The paper also focuses on collision avoidance for unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs), which is a topic related to robotics (cs.RO). The paper uses theoretical developments to ensure that multiple safety constraints are simultaneously satisfied in a decentralized manner, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also validates the theoretical developments in a simulation, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG).
